import { React, useState } from 'react'; import '../../assets/style/FlightHistoryCard.css'; import { calculateDuration } from '../../utils/util.js'; import { formatDate } from '../../utils/util.js'; const FlightHistoryCard = ({ flight }) => { const { flightName, flightNumber, scheduleDateTime, actualOffBlockTime, expectedTimeGateOpen, airlineName, expectedTimeGateClosing, expectedTimeBoarding, estimatedLandingTime, actualLandingTime, prefixIATA, aircraftRegistration, departureCode, route: { destinations }, aircraftType } = flight; const [detailsVisible, setDetailsVisible] = useState(false); const [arrivalCode] = destinations; const flightDuration = calculateDuration(estimatedLandingTime || expectedTimeBoarding || actualOffBlockTime, scheduleDateTime); const boardingTime = expectedTimeBoarding ? new Date(expectedTimeBoarding).toLocaleTimeString() : 'TBA'; const gateOpens = expectedTimeGateOpen ? new Date(expectedTimeGateOpen).toLocaleTimeString() : 'TBA'; const landingTime = estimatedLandingTime || actualLandingTime ? new Date(estimatedLandingTime || actualLandingTime).toLocaleTimeString() : 'TBA'; const totalSlots = 5; const filledPackages = flight.farePackage?.length || 0; const emptySlots = totalSlots - filledPackages; const emptyPackages = Array(emptySlots).fill({ packageName: '', price: '' }); const allPackages = [...flight.farePackage || [], ...emptyPackages]; const toggleDetails = () => { setDetailsVisible(!detailsVisible); }; return (

{departureTime}

 - 

{arrivalTime}

{airlineName || prefixIATA}
{destinations?.length + ' Stop' || 'nonstop'}
{flightDuration}
{departureCode}  to  {arrivalCode}
{flightName}
{allPackages.map((pkg, index) => (
{pkg.packageName ? ( <>
${pkg.price}
{pkg.packageName}
) : null}
))}
{detailsVisible && (
Boarding

Boarding Time: {boardingTime}

Gate Opens: {gateOpens}

Landing: {landingTime}

Aircraft

Registration: {aircraftRegistration}

Type: {aircraftType?.iataMain}

Flight

Number: {flightNumber}

Name: {flightName}

Type: {aircraftType?.iataMain}

)}
); }; export default FlightHistoryCard;
